; Coverage for commodity.cc tag lexical comparison
; Two lots with different tags exercises the string comparison of tags
; "alpha" < "beta" in lexicographic order

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL {$150.00} (alpha)
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/15 Buy More
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$150.00} (beta)
    Assets:Checking

test bal --lots Assets:Brokerage
10 AAPL {$150} (alpha)
5 AAPL {$150} (beta)  Assets:Brokerage
end test
